Package venice.hub

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    ConsoleControl
    Reads user input from console, parses commands and calls appropriate methods from VeniceHub.
    DiskReader
    Reads data from disk.
    DiskWriter
    Writes compressed data to disk.
    IIOReader
    Listens to InstantIO namespace and receives data from slots.
    IIOWriter
    Writes data to InstantIO namespace.
    PortReader
    Reads data from a TCP port.
    RPCControl
    Sets up a RPC server for controlling VeniceHub via RPC.
    RSBReader
    Reads data from RSB.
    RSBWriter
    Writes data to RSB scope.
    VeniceControl
    Control classes are the user interfaces to VeniceHub.
    VeniceHub
    Starts and stops all other threads.
    VeniceReader
    Reads data from source.
    VeniceWriter
    Abstract class for writing data from TTEQueue to a target.
